data.description: This 3 bedroom stick built home has lots of great features including a metal roof, hardwood floors, and an EZ Breeze screen room. The attached garage was finished off and would be perfect for a primary suite. The detached garage and shed provide ample storage. Large lot with no HOA or city taxes!! While some improvements are necessary, envisioning its potential correctly will reveal a hidden gem. This diamond in the rough would serve as the perfect place for a home occupation, a starter home, or a promising investment venture! This would make a great house for a home occupation!
